Package: furvdailyqc
Type: Package
Title: Quality Control Functions for Tmax, Tmin and Precipitation Daily Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author:Alba Gilabert
Maintainer: Alba Gilabert <alba.gilabert@urv.cat>
Description: Package to QC daily maximum (Tmax) and minimum temperatures (Tmin) 
    and daily precipitation (RR).
    A set of seven functions: to detect big errors (for Tmax, Tmin and RR data), 
    to detect rounding problems (for Tmax, Tmin and RR data), to detect duplicate
    dates (for Tmax, Tmin and RR data), to detect climatic outliers (for Tmax, Tmin
    and RR data), to detect too large interdiurnal differences (Tmax and Tmin), to
    detect internal consistency between Tmax and Tmin and a tolerance test (Tmax 
    and Tmin).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
